text: Warren Petersen is an American politician. He is a member of the Arizona State Senate and was a member of the Arizona House of Representatives. He is the President of the Senate in 2024. He was also Majority Leader of the House of Representatives in 2018-2019.https://azcapitoltimes.com/news/2018/11/07/arizona-house- republicans-choose-rep-bowers-to-lead-them/ ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Arizona Legislature Category:Politicians from Arizona Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
title: Warren Petersen
